---
title: Veggie Burritos (v) with Tomato Salad, Lime and Soured Cream
description: Quick, fresh, and packed with veg, our vegetarian take on the Mexican classic is the perfect midweek treat. Seasoned with our delicious Mississippi spice mix, rolled up, covered with cheese and baked until crisp and golden, the flavours in our burritos are hard to beat. Served with a fresh tomato salad and cooling soured cream, we recommend serving everything up in the middle of your table and getting everyone to tuck in.
